coefficients result from <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mi>α</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo><m:mn>35980373244182</m:mn><m:mspace width="4pt"/><m:mtext>and</m:mtext><m:mspace width="4pt"/><m:mi>β</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo><m:mn>78210638474440</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</para>
        <para id="id265962">The inverse of these formulas which will give <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>α</m:mi></m:math> and <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>β</m:mi></m:math> from
